{
  "stem": "1826.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found work there, and I-- What kind of work?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liquor.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Liquor.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found my job there thanks to the fact that I knew Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because some of these occupants, the Russians-- and this was Ukraine-- as they did not know Polish, and they didn't know Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did director of a factory of liquor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out that the director is looking for somebody with the knowledge of Russian, and he was looking for a secretary-- a girl secretary.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I found out about that, and I came to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very disappointed that not a girl came ask for the job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But since he needed somebody, he couldn't function somehow without, so he accepted me as the secretary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's at the factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When in Lemberg, well, we found-- my brother also came to Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he worked also somewhere on the railroad office or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they-- the Russian authorities, the Soviet authorities, started to-- all these people who came from Poland, all this, as they're called, the refugees.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The refugees, they took, or started to take them away, all the way into deep Siberia as for work, you know, for work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And anybody who, who couldn't prove that he lived there before the war was taken by force and taken away all the way to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, because I did know the Russian language, somehow I managed to persuade them and convince them-- then convince them that I lived there before, and I got a passport, the passport.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anybody-- any of the refugees who did not have a passport, a Soviet passport already was taken away by force and had to-- back to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, it was-- this was in 1939, 1940, and 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
